	measure 'Original Cost - Rep (TH)' = ```
			
			VAR closePeriod =
			    MAX ( 'Period'[Period] )
			
			RETURN
			    CALCULATE (
			        IF (
				SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "SCD Base",
				SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Base] ),
			 SUMX (
			        'Securities Transaction GA Fact',
			        'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Local (D)]  * 'Fx Rate DQ'[Rep Rate]
			    )
				),
			        ALL ( 'Period' ),
			        'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[As Of Period] <= closePeriod
			    )
			
			```
