	measure 'Infor Acquisition Rate (Sec Trans)' = ```
			
			VAR Amt =SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Local unsigned] )
			VAR local =
			    IF ( Amt = 0, 1, Amt )
			RETURN
			    SWITCH (
			        SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ),
			        "SCD Base",
			        SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Base unsigned] ) / local,    
			        SUMX (
			                'Securities Transaction GA Fact',
			                'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Local unsigned] * 'Fx Rate DQ'[Rep Rate] / Local
			            )
			    )
			
			/*
			var local =  if(SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Local] )=0,1,SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Local] ))
			Return
			IF (
			    SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "SCD Base",
			        SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - Base] )/local,
			    IF (
			        SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "USD",
			            SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - USD] )/local,
			        IF (
			            SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "CAD",
			                SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - CAD] )/local,
			
			            IF (
			                SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "Company",
			                    SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - FUNC] )/local,
			                    SUM ( 'Securities Transaction GA Fact'[Cost Value - HKD] )/local
			                )
			            )
			        )
			    )
			    */
			```
		formatString: 0.000000
		lineageTag: 36a7a52e-19a4-473f-b7fc-b5bc4b962a65

